Eau Claire.Antique Emporium: The Antique Emporium is a historic Masonic building located on the corner of South Barstow and Main Streets in Eau Claire, Wisconsin. It was built in 1899 and listed on the National Register of Historic Places in 2007 (as: Eau Claire Masonic Temple). The Masonic bodies that once met there relocated in 1927 to the Temple of Free Masonry on Graham Avenue.
